text: Gail Davenport (born March 1, 1949) is an American politician who has served in the Georgia State Senate from the 44th district since 2011. She previously served in the Georgia State Senate from 2007 to 2009. ==References== Category:1949 births Category:Living people Category:Georgia (U.S. state) state senators Category:Georgia (U.S. state) Democrats
